Statistical Inference in Linguistics
Roland Schäfer, Freie Universität Berlin

My CC-BY text book about statistics in linguistics. Uses the template
from Language Science Press (my preferred publisher) in an adapted
form for use with knitr.

---

The required Inconsolata-g font can be obtained here:
http://www.fantascienza.net/leonardo/ar/inconsolatag/inconsolata-g_font.zip

On Ubuntu:
sudo mkdir /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts
sudo cp Inconsolatar.ttf /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts/
sudo fc-cache -fv
